---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuizCard from '../../components/QuizCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 3: 力と質量、密度">
  <h1>Week 3: 力と質量、密度</h1>

  <!-- ===== Section 1: 密度 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>📦 密度ってなんだろう？</h2>
    
    <div class="intro-box">
      <strong>🤔 なぜ鉄は重く、綿は軽い？</strong><br/>
      同じ大きさ（体積）で比べたときの「ぎっしり度」が違うから！
    </div>

    <div class="formula-box main-formula">
      <span class="big-formula">ρ = m / V</span>
      <p>密度 ＝ 質量 ÷ 体積</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 公式三変形 -->
    <div class="formula-trio">
      <div class="formula-card">
        <div class="formula-icon">📐</div>
        <div class="formula-text">ρ = m ÷ V</div>
        <div class="formula-desc">密度を求める</div>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-card">
        <div class="formula-icon">⚖️</div>
        <div class="formula-text">m = ρ × V</div>
        <div class="formula-desc">質量を求める</div>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-card">
        <div class="formula-icon">📦</div>
        <div class="formula-text">V = m ÷ ρ</div>
        <div class="formula-desc">体積を求める</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="symbol-table">
      <table>
        <tr><th>記号</th><th>意味</th><th>SI単位</th><th>CGS単位</th></tr>
        <tr><td>ρ（ロー）</td><td>密度</td><td>kg/m³</td><td>g/cm³</td></tr>
        <tr><td>m</td><td>質量</td><td>kg</td><td>g</td></tr>
        <tr><td>V</td><td>体積</td><td>m³</td><td>cm³</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h3>代表的な物質の密度</h3>
    <div class="density-table">
      <table>
        <tr><th>物質</th><th>密度 (g/cm³)</th><th>水に入れると</th></tr>
        <tr><td>水</td><td>1.00</td><td>（基準）</td></tr>
        <tr class="float"><td>木</td><td>約 0.5</td><td>🔼 浮く</td></tr>
        <tr class="sink"><td>アルミ</td><td>2.70</td><td>🔽 沈む</td></tr>
        <tr class="sink"><td>鉄</td><td>7.87</td><td>🔽 沈む</td></tr>
        <tr class="sink"><td>金</td><td>19.32</td><td>🔽 沈む</td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="table-note">📌 密度 < 1.0 → 水に浮く！</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 2: 練習 - 密度 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 1：密度の計算</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">公式の3変形を使い分けよう</p>

    <QuizCard 
      id="1"
      question="質量 500 g、体積 100 cm³ の物体の密度"
      answer="5.0"
      answerUnit="g/cm³"
      steps={[
        "密度を求める → ρ = m/V",
        "ρ = 500 ÷ 100",
        "= <strong>5.0 g/cm³</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="2"
      question="密度 2.5 g/cm³、体積 20 cm³ の物体の質量"
      answer="50"
      answerUnit="g"
      steps={[
        "質量を求める → m = ρV",
        "m = 2.5 × 20",
        "= <strong>50 g</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="3"
      question="密度 7.8 g/cm³、質量 39 g の金属の体積"
      answer="5.0"
      answerUnit="cm³"
      steps={[
        "体積を求める → V = m/ρ",
        "V = 39 ÷ 7.8",
        "= <strong>5.0 cm³</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="3つ目の変形！V = m ÷ ρ"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 3: 質量と重さの違い ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>⚖️ 質量と重さは違う！</h2>
    
    <p class="transition-text">
      密度は「物質そのものの特性」でした。<br/>
      では、その物質が<strong>地球や月にいるとき</strong>、どんな力を受けるでしょう？<br/>
      → それが「重力（重さ）」です！
    </p>

    <div class="danger-box">
      <span class="danger-icon">⚠️</span>
      <span>最重要！「質量」と「重さ」を混同しないで！</span>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-cards">
      <div class="comp-card mass-card">
        <h4>質量 (m)</h4>
        <div class="comp-icon">⚛️</div>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>意味：</strong>物体の「中身の量」</li>
          <li><strong>単位：</strong>kg</li>
          <li><strong>場所で変わる？</strong>❌ 変わらない</li>
          <li><strong>月に行くと：</strong>同じ！</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="comp-card weight-card">
        <h4>重さ・重力 (W)</h4>
        <div class="comp-icon">⬇️</div>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>意味：</strong>星に引っ張られる力</li>
          <li><strong>単位：</strong>N（ニュートン）</li>
          <li><strong>場所で変わる？</strong>⭕ 変わる</li>
          <li><strong>月に行くと：</strong>約 1/6</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="formula-box">
      <span class="big-formula">W = mg</span>
      <p>重力 ＝ 質量 × 重力加速度</p>
    </div>

    <div class="g-table">
      <table>
        <tr><th>場所</th><th>重力加速度 g</th><th>備考</th></tr>
        <tr><td>地球（地表）</td><td>9.8 m/s² ≈ <strong>10</strong></td><td>計算では10を使う</td></tr>
        <tr><td>月</td><td>約 1.6 m/s²</td><td>地球の <strong>1/6</strong></td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 4: 月の比較（可視化） ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>🌙 月への旅行で考えよう</h2>

    <div class="moon-comparison">
      <div class="planet-card earth">
        <div class="planet-icon">🌍</div>
        <h4>地球</h4>
        <div class="astronaut">👨‍🚀</div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="label">質量：</span>
          <span class="value">60 kg</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value-row highlight">
          <span class="label">重さ：</span>
          <span class="value">600 N</span>
        </div>
        <p class="calc">W = 60 × 10 = 600 N</p>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow-container">
        <div class="travel-arrow">🚀</div>
      </div>

      <div class="planet-card moon">
        <div class="planet-icon">🌙</div>
        <h4>月</h4>
        <div class="astronaut">👨‍🚀</div>
        <div class="value-row same">
          <span class="label">質量：</span>
          <span class="value">60 kg</span>
          <span class="badge">同じ！</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value-row highlight">
          <span class="label">重さ：</span>
          <span class="value">100 N</span>
        </div>
        <p class="calc">W = 60 × 1.6 ≈ 100 N</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="trap-warning">
      <h4>🚨 陥りやすい罠！</h4>
      <p>「月に行ったら質量も1/6になる」→ <strong>❌ 間違い！</strong></p>
      <p>質量は物体の固有の性質。どこに行っても変わらない！</p>
      <p>変わるのは<strong>重力（重さ）</strong>だけ！</p>
    </div>

    <h3>測定器具の違い</h3>
    <div class="tool-comparison">
      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-icon">🔧</div>
        <h5>バネばかり</h5>
        <p>測るもの：<strong>重さ（重力）</strong></p>
        <p>月では：値が<span class="down">小さくなる</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-icon">⚖️</div>
        <h5>上皿天秤</h5>
        <p>測るもの：<strong>質量</strong></p>
        <p>月では：<span class="same-text">同じ値</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 5: 練習 - 重力 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 2：重力の計算</h2>

    <QuizCard 
      id="4"
      question="質量 5 kg の物体の重力（g = 10 m/s²）"
      answer="50"
      answerUnit="N"
      steps={[
        "W = mg",
        "W = 5 × 10",
        "= <strong>50 N</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="5"
      question="質量 200 g のリンゴの重力（g = 10 m/s²）"
      answer="2"
      answerUnit="N"
      steps={[
        "まず単位をSIに：200 g = 0.2 kg",
        "W = mg = 0.2 × 10",
        "= <strong>2 N</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="g → kg に換算してから計算！"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="6"
      question="月で重さが 10 N の物体、地球での重さ"
      answer="60"
      answerUnit="N"
      steps={[
        "月の重力 = 地球の 1/6",
        "地球での重さ = 月での重さ × 6",
        "= 10 × 6 = <strong>60 N</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="7"
      question="重力 30 N を受けている物体の質量（g = 10）"
      answer="3"
      answerUnit="kg"
      steps={[
        "W = mg より m = W/g",
        "m = 30 ÷ 10",
        "= <strong>3 kg</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="公式を変形：m = W ÷ g"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 6: 陷阱題専區 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section trap-section">
    <h2>🚨 陷阱チェック：質量 vs 重さ</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">この問題、間違える人が本当に多い！</p>

    <QuizCard 
      id="8"
      question="宇宙飛行士の地球での質量は 72 kg。月に行ったら質量は？"
      answer="72"
      answerUnit="kg"
      steps={[
        "🚨 陷阱注意！",
        "質量は「物体に含まれる物質の量」",
        "場所が変わっても <strong>質量は変わらない</strong>",
        "答え：<strong>72 kg</strong>（同じ！）"
      ]}
      hint="間違えやすい！重さと質量を混同しないで"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="9"
      question="地球で 600 N の重力を受ける人、月での重力は？"
      answer="100"
      answerUnit="N"
      steps={[
        "月の重力加速度 = 地球の 1/6",
        "月での重力 = 600 ÷ 6",
        "= <strong>100 N</strong>"
      ]}
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 7: バネの力（フックの法則） ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>🔩 バネの力（フックの法則）</h2>

    <p class="intro-text">バネを引っ張ると、元に戻ろうとする力が生まれます。</p>

    <div class="formula-box">
      <span class="big-formula">F = kx</span>
      <p>弾性力 ＝ バネ定数 × 伸び</p>
    </div>

    <div class="symbol-table">
      <table>
        <tr><th>記号</th><th>意味</th><th>単位</th></tr>
        <tr><td>F</td><td>弾性力（バネの力）</td><td>N</td></tr>
        <tr><td>k</td><td>バネ定数（硬さ）</td><td>N/m</td></tr>
        <tr><td>x</td><td>伸び（自然長からの変化）</td><td>m</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="spring-demo">
      <div class="spring-visual">
        <div class="spring-base">📍</div>
        <div class="spring-coil">〰️〰️〰️</div>
        <div class="spring-weight">🔴</div>
      </div>
      <div class="spring-labels">
        <p>自然長からの伸び = <strong>x</strong></p>
        <p>重りの重力 = バネの弾性力</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-box">
      <strong>💡 バネばかりの原理</strong>
      <p>物体をバネに吊るすと、重力 W とバネの力 F がつり合う：</p>
      <p class="formula-inline"><strong>W = F = kx</strong></p>
      <p>伸び x を測れば、重力（重さ）がわかる！</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 8: 練習 - バネ ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 3：バネの計算</h2>

    <QuizCard 
      id="10"
      question="バネ定数 50 N/m のバネが 0.2 m 伸びた時の弾性力"
      answer="10"
      answerUnit="N"
      steps={[
        "F = kx",
        "F = 50 × 0.2",
        "= <strong>10 N</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="11"
      question="バネ定数 25 N/m のバネに物体を吊るしたら 0.24 m 伸びた。物体の重力は？"
      answer="6"
      answerUnit="N"
      steps={[
        "つり合い状態：重力 W = 弾性力 F",
        "F = kx = 25 × 0.24",
        "= <strong>6 N</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="12"
      question="問11のバネと物体を月に持っていくと、伸びは？"
      answer="0.04"
      answerUnit="m"
      steps={[
        "月では重力が 1/6 になる",
        "W_月 = 6 ÷ 6 = 1 N",
        "F = kx より x = F/k",
        "x = 1 ÷ 25 = <strong>0.04 m</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="バネ定数 k は場所で変わらない！"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="13"
      question="問11の物体の質量は？（地球 g = 10）"
      answer="0.6"
      answerUnit="kg"
      steps={[
        "地球での重力 W = 6 N",
        "W = mg より m = W/g",
        "m = 6 ÷ 10 = <strong>0.6 kg</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="14"
      question="問11の物体を月に持っていった時の質量は？"
      answer="0.6"
      answerUnit="kg"
      steps={[
        "🚨 また陷阱！",
        "質量は場所で変わらない",
        "答え：<strong>0.6 kg</strong>（同じ！）"
      ]}
      hint="2回目の陷阱！もう間違えないよね？"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 9: まとめ ===== -->
  <section class="content-section summary-section">
    <h2>📝 今日のまとめ</h2>
    <div class="summary-grid">
      <div class="summary-item">
        <span class="summary-icon">📦</span>
        <span>密度：<strong>ρ = m/V</strong>（3変形を使い分ける）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-item">
        <span class="summary-icon">⬇️</span>
        <span>重力：<strong>W = mg</strong></span>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-item">
        <span class="summary-icon">🔩</span>
        <span>バネの力：<strong>F = kx</strong></span>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-item warning">
        <span class="summary-icon">⚠️</span>
        <span><strong>質量は場所で変わらない、重さは変わる！</strong></span>
      </div>
      <div class="summary-item">
        <span class="summary-icon">🌙</span>
        <span>月の重力加速度は地球の <strong>1/6</strong></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week02/" class="nav-btn secondary">← Week 2</a>
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week04/" class="nav-btn">Week 4 へ →</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ===== 基本スタイル ===== */
  .content-section {
    margin: 40px 0;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    color: #1e293b;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #3b82f6;
  }

  .section-desc {
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .intro-text, .transition-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ===== 導入ボックス ===== */
  .intro-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  /* ===== 公式ボックス ===== */
  .formula-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
    border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .big-formula {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d4ed8;
  }

  .formula-box p {
    margin: 8px 0 0;
    color: #475569;
  }

  /* ===== 公式三変形カード ===== */
  .formula-trio {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .formula-card {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .formula-card:hover {
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .formula-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .formula-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1e293b;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  .formula-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ===== テーブル ===== */
  .symbol-table table, .g-table table, .density-table table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .symbol-table th, .symbol-table td,
  .g-table th, .g-table td,
  .density-table th, .density-table td {
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .symbol-table th, .g-table th, .density-table th {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .density-table .float { background: #dcfce7; }
  .density-table .sink { background: #fee2e2; }
  .table-note { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #059669; margin-top: 8px; }

  /* ===== 危険ボックス ===== */
  .danger-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
    border: 2px solid #ef4444;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .danger-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ===== 質量vs重さ比較カード ===== */
  .comparison-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .comp-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .comp-card h4 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .comp-icon {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .comp-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .comp-card li {
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .mass-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5 0%, #d1fae5 100%);
    border: 2px solid #10b981;
  }

  .weight-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
    border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
  }

  /* ===== 月比較 ===== */
  .moon-comparison {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .planet-card {
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .planet-card.earth {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%);
    border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
  }

  .planet-card.moon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #e5e7eb 100%);
    border: 2px solid #6b7280;
  }

  .planet-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .planet-card h4 {
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  .astronaut {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }

  .value-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 0;
  }

  .value-row.highlight .value {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #dc2626;
  }

